title: 2020 Week 14 Preview
itunes:title: 2020 Week 14 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview each upcoming game of week 14 starting with the primetime game between the Steelers and Bills (2:05). The Ravens travel to Cleveland to face the Browns (8:45) and Gregg is excited about the Chiefs-Dolphins game (15:46). Marc is looking forward to watching the frisky New York Giants (25:58) and Washington at San Francisco (31:20).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
